A suspected thug was on Friday night shot dead by police officers in Makadara area. Isaac Kamau was gunned down by Dagoretti OCPD Rashid Mohamed when he demanded money at a gun point. &nbsp;Rashid was driving along Jogoo Road at around 10.30pm, when the suspect confronted him with a Ceska pistol. &quot;On reaching Hamsa stage, Rashid was confronted by a lone gun man. He acted first and shot dead the suspect who was later identified as Isaac Kamau Wangura,&quot; police report, which further states that the gun recovered was from another officer&nbsp;who was interdicted in 2015 for losing it.